	<header class="entry-header">
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on">Posted on </span><time class="entry-date updated" datetime="2015-02-18T05:00:31+00:00" pubdate>Wednesday, February 18, 2015</time>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
		
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/season-3-episode-6-how-to-become-your-spouses-best-friend.html" title="Permalink to Season 3, Episode 6: How to Become Your Spouse’s Best Friend [Podcast]" rel="bookmark">Season 3, Episode 6: How to Become Your Spouse’s Best Friend [Podcast]</a></h1>
