		<p class="first-child "><span title="W" class="dropcap">W</span>elcome to <a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/podcast-season-3" title="This Is Your Life Season 3">Season 3</a>, Episode 6 of the <em><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/podcast-season-3" title="This Is Your Life Season 3">This Is Your Life</a></em> podcast. In this second episode, <a href="http://michelecushatt.com/" title="Michele Cushatt’s Website">Michele Cushatt</a> and I discuss what every leader needs to know about their relationships.</p>
