<article id="post-28584" class="post-28584 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-leadership tag-communication tag-persuasion tag-powerless-words tag-words">
	<header class="entry-header">
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on">Posted on </span><time class="entry-date updated" datetime="2015-02-13T05:00:31+00:00" pubdate>Friday, February 13, 2015</time>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
		
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/giving-up-power.html" title="Permalink to 3 Ways You’re Giving up Power with Your Words" rel="bookmark">3 Ways You’re Giving up Power with Your Words</a></h1>
		<h3 class="getnoticed-entry-subtitle">How the Way You Speak Can Sabotage Your Success</h3>		
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<aside class='sharebar'>
<span class="share-social share-facebook"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2Fgiving-up-power.html" class="button" title="Share on Facebook" data-url="http://michaelhyatt.com/giving-up-power.html" data-threshold="10" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><i></i><span>Share</span></a><span class="count"></span></span>
<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-social share-tweet"><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?original_referer=http%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2Fgiving-up-power.html&source=tweetbutton&text=3+Ways+You%E2%80%99re+Giving+up+Power+with+Your+Words&url=http%3A%2F%2Fmhyatt.us%2F1EiEJny&via=michaelhyatt" class="button" title="Tweet this Post" data-url="http://michaelhyatt.com/giving-up-power.html" data-threshold="10" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><i></i><span>Tweet</span></a><span class="count"></span></span>
<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-social share-linkedin"><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=http%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2Fgiving-up-power.html&title=3+Ways+You%E2%80%99re+Giving+up+Power+with+Your+Words&source=Get+Noticed%21+Theme" class="button" title="Share on LinkedIn" data-url="http://michaelhyatt.com/giving-up-power.html" data-threshold="" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><i></i><span>Share</span></a><span class="count"></span></span>
<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-social share-buffer"><a href="http://bufferapp.com/add?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2Fgiving-up-power.html&text=3+Ways+You%E2%80%99re+Giving+up+Power+with+Your+Words&source=getnoticedtheme&count=vertical" class="button" title="Share with Buffer" data-url="http://michaelhyatt.com/giving-up-power.html" data-threshold="5" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><i></i><span>Buffer</span></a><span class="count"></span></span>
<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-print"><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/giving-up-power.html#print" class="button"><span>print</span></a></span>
<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-email"><a href="mailto:?subject=3%20Ways%20You%E2%80%99re%20Giving%20up%20Power%20with%20Your%20Words&amp;body=Hey%2C%0D%0A%0D%0AI%20wanted%20to%20share%20this%20post%20by%20Michael%20Hyatt%20with%20you.%0D%0A%0D%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2Fgiving-up-power.html%0D%0A%0D%0AThanks%21" class="button"><span>email</span></a></span></aside>
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p class="first-child "><span title="O" class="dropcap">O</span>ur words can be powerful tools to accomplish our goals. But sometimes the things we say can sabotage our success.</p>
<p><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/giving-up-power.html"><img width="760" height="507" src="http://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/istock_000029051252_medium-760x507.jpg" class="featured-image wp-post-image" alt="keys in the hand" /></a></p><div class="photo-credit">Courtesy of iStock/anyaberkut</div>
<p>I have led, counseled, and mentored people for decades now. One thing I’ve noticed time and again is how much power our words possess.</p>
<p>Whether we’re speaking, blogging, selling, or debating, we rely on our words to pave the way to success. But they can also block our path if we’re not careful.</p>
	</div>


	
