<article id="post-28565" class="post-28565 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-podcast tag-arrogance tag-decision-making tag-disorganization tag-leadership tag-lousy-leaders tag-over-confidence">
	<header class="entry-header">
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on">Posted on </span><time class="entry-date updated" datetime="2015-02-11T05:00:38+00:00" pubdate>Wednesday, February 11, 2015</time>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
		
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/season-3-episode-5-top-10-characteristics-of-lousy-leaders.html" title="Permalink to Season 3, Episode 5: The Top-10 Characteristics of Lousy Leaders [Podcast]" rel="bookmark">Season 3, Episode 5: The Top-10 Characteristics of Lousy Leaders [Podcast]</a></h1>
		<h3 class="getnoticed-entry-subtitle">We Most Often Learn the Most from Those Who Lead the Worst</h3>		
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<aside class='sharebar'>
<span class="share-social share-facebook"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2Fseason-3-episode-5-top-10-characteristics-of-lousy-leaders.html" class="button" title="Share on Facebook" data-url="http://michaelhyatt.com/season-3-episode-5-top-10-characteristics-of-lousy-leaders.html" data-threshold="10" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><i></i><span>Share</span></a><span class="count"></span></span>
