<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-email"><a href="mailto:?subject=Season%203%2C%20Episode%205%3A%20The%20Top-10%20Characteristics%20of%20Lousy%20Leaders%20%5BPodcast%5D&amp;body=Hey%2C%0D%0A%0D%0AI%20wanted%20to%20share%20this%20post%20by%20Michael%20Hyatt%20with%20you.%0D%0A%0D%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2Fseason-3-episode-5-top-10-characteristics-of-lousy-leaders.html%0D%0A%0D%0AThanks%21" class="button"><span>email</span></a></span></aside>
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p class="first-child "><span title="W" class="dropcap">W</span>elcome to <a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/podcast-season-3" title="This Is Your Life Season 3">Season 3</a>, Episode 5 of the <em><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/podcast-season-3" title="This Is Your Life Season 3">This Is Your Life</a></em> podcast. In this second episode, <a href="http://michelecushatt.com/" title="Michele Cushatt’s Website">Michele Cushatt</a> and I discuss the top-10 characteristics of lousy leaders.</p>
<p><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/season-3-episode-5-top-10-characteristics-of-lousy-leaders.html"><img width="760" height="380" src="http://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Season-3-Episode-5-Artwork-V1-760x380.jpg" class="featured-image wp-post-image" alt="Season-3-Episode-5-Artwork-V1" /></a></p>
<p>Follow the major news stories on crises in business, politics, diplomacy, whatever, and it’s impossible to miss that most are crises of leadership. Unsurprisingly, we see the same failures and mistakes over and over. Here are the ten I most often notice.</p>
	</div>


	
