		<h3 class="getnoticed-entry-subtitle">3 Ways CoSchedule Helps Me Get Big Results</h3>		
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<aside class='sharebar'>
<span class="share-social share-facebook"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2Fmaster-social-media.html" class="button" title="Share on Facebook" data-url="http://michaelhyatt.com/master-social-media.html" data-threshold="10" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><i></i><span>Share</span></a><span class="count"></span></span>
