	<div class="entry-content">
		<p class="first-child "><span title="W" class="dropcap">W</span>hen I first started blogging social media was practically nonexistent. Now it’s a major driver of traffic.</p>
<p><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/master-social-media.html"><img width="760" height="475" src="http://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/coschedule1-760x475.png" class="featured-image wp-post-image" alt="coschedule1" /></a></p>
<p>Unfortunately, with all the new platforms and strategies, it’s more complicated and time-consuming than ever. Or, at least, it was until I found <a href="http://coschedule.com/michael-hyatt">CoSchedule</a>.</p>
