	<header class="entry-header">
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on">Posted on </span><time class="entry-date updated" datetime="2015-02-05T05:00:44+00:00" pubdate>Thursday, February 5, 2015</time>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
		
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/2015-reader-survey.html" title="Permalink to Please Take My 2015 Reader Survey" rel="bookmark">Please Take My 2015 Reader Survey</a></h1>
		<h3 class="getnoticed-entry-subtitle">Help Me Create Content That Serves Your Needs</h3>		
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<aside class='sharebar'>
<span class="share-social share-facebook"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2F2015-reader-survey.html" class="button" title="Share on Facebook" data-url="http://michaelhyatt.com/2015-reader-survey.html" data-threshold="10" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><i></i><span>Share</span></a><span class="count"></span></span>
<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-social share-tweet"><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?original_referer=http%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2F2015-reader-survey.html&source=tweetbutton&text=Please+Take+My+2015+Reader+Survey&url=http%3A%2F%2Fmhyatt.us%2F1Dg8Y08&via=michaelhyatt" class="button" title="Tweet this Post" data-url="http://michaelhyatt.com/2015-reader-survey.html" data-threshold="10" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><i></i><span>Tweet</span></a><span class="count"></span></span>
<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-social share-linkedin"><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=http%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2F2015-reader-survey.html&title=Please+Take+My+2015+Reader+Survey&source=Get+Noticed%21+Theme" class="button" title="Share on LinkedIn" data-url="http://michaelhyatt.com/2015-reader-survey.html" data-threshold="" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><i></i><span>Share</span></a><span class="count"></span></span>
<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-social share-buffer"><a href="http://bufferapp.com/add?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2F2015-reader-survey.html&text=Please+Take+My+2015+Reader+Survey&source=getnoticedtheme&count=vertical" class="button" title="Share with Buffer" data-url="http://michaelhyatt.com/2015-reader-survey.html" data-threshold="5" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><i></i><span>Buffer</span></a><span class="count"></span></span>
<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-print"><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/2015-reader-survey.html#print" class="button"><span>print</span></a></span>
<span class='sep'> | </span>
<span class="share-email"><a href="mailto:?subject=Please%20Take%20My%202015%20Reader%20Survey&amp;body=Hey%2C%0D%0A%0D%0AI%20wanted%20to%20share%20this%20post%20by%20Michael%20Hyatt%20with%20you.%0D%0A%0D%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fmichaelhyatt.com%2F2015-reader-survey.html%0D%0A%0D%0AThanks%21" class="button"><span>email</span></a></span></aside>
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p class="first-child "><span title="I" class="dropcap">I</span> want to ensure my platform does the best possible job of answering your needs and interests. And that means I need to know more about <em>you</em>. To do that, I’ve created my <a href="https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/ZRHL2ML" target="_blank">2015 Reader Survey</a>.</p>
<p><a href="http://michaelhyatt.com/2015-reader-survey.html"><img width="760" height="507" src="http://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/iStock_000030700910_Medium-760x507.jpg" class="featured-image wp-post-image" alt="Computer key showing the word Feedback." /></a></p><div class="photo-credit">Courtesy of iStock/scyther5</div>
<p>Would you please take a few minutes to fill out the survey? By doing so, you will ultimately be helping yourself. Why? Because you will be helping me create content even more interesting and relevant to you.</p>
	</div>


	
